# ğŸš« Where you usually CANNOT use your SSO

Important reality check.

Your self-hosted SSO generally **cannot replace**:

* Google account login for Gmail
* Microsoft account
* random third-party sites

Because those services donâ€™t trust your IdP.

SSO works when:

âœ… you control the app
âœ… or the app allows custom OIDC/SAML

